She is currently a Business Development Manager responsible for driving NXP's processors and connectivity leadership and growth in the consumer market. Prior to this role, Sujata worked in business development and product marketing for NXP's i.MX applications processors. She earned a Bachelor of Science in Electrical Engineering from the University of Texas at Austin.








