Home





Welcome to the home of the Open Knowledge Foundation’s working group on Open Product Data. A community project working to build a public database of product data


Join the Group

 




Imagine a database containing all the commercialised products in the world


Imagine using barcodes to  empower consumers  with valuable information about the products they buy


Imagine building the database and applications consumers need to make informed decisions

Visit Product Open Data to see what we’ve done, join the mailing list to find out how you can get involved and follow us on twitter





